<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَيَجِبَانِ فِي العُمْرِ مَرَّةً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- بِخَمْسَةِ شُرُوطٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> الإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَالعَقْلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- فَلَا يَصِحَّانِ مِنْ كَافِرٍ وَمَجْنُونٍ؛ وَلَوْ أَحْرَمَ عَنْهُ وَلِيُّهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَالبُلُوغُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَكَمَالُ الحُرِّيَّةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- لَكِنْ يَصِحَّانِ مِنَ الصَّغِيرِ، وَالرَّقِيقِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَيُحْرِمُ عَنِ الصَّغِيرِ وَلِيُّهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَلَا يُجْزِئَانِ عَنْ حَجَّةِ الإِسْلَامِ وَعُمْرَتِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنْ بَلَغَ الصَّغِيرُ أَوْ عَتَقَ الرَّقِيقُ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أ) قَبْلَ الوُقُوفِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">ب) أَوْ بَعْدَهُ إِنْ عَادَ فَوَقَفَ فِي وَقْتِهِ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أَجْزَأَهُ عَنْ حَجَّةِ الإِسْلَامِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَالخَامِسُ: الِاسْتِطَاعَةُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>